title: Steve Wilkos Is He A Molester
description:
IS HE A MOLESTER?

A chilling allegation? Alex has been accused of some of the most heinous molestation charges Steve's ever heard. His ex-wife, Kaila, first launched the investigation after their 5-year-old daughter made an alarming confession. Alex's sister, Leslie, says that she heard her own confession from Kaila, admitting she made the entire story up to get back at Alex. This story is no joke, and Steve's going to find the truth behind it all.
